folder: Fillmore Avenue & Marine Parkway, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Fillmore Avenue, west from Marine Parkway, showing a W. P. A. highway project. The houses seen in the right background are on Stuart Street and those in the left background are on Brown Street. View 2 shows another section of the project.
August 13, 1935
Views 1,2
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
